Class HumanPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • model.Player
        • model.HumanPlayer

  • public class HumanPlayer
extends Player
    Allows a human user to play a game of Risk. Sends messages back and forth to the GUI to record the user's decisions and interactions.
    Author:
    Steven Broussard, Elizabeth Harris, Jeremy Jalnos, Becca Simon
